Title: Equivalence of Weyl Vacuum and Normal Ordered Vacuum in the Moyal

QuantizationAuthors: Takao Koikawa

Comments: 8 pages

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 107 (2002) 1061-1067

We study the features of the vacuum of the harmonic oscillator in the Moyalquantization. Two vacua are defined, one with the normal ordering and the otherwith the Weyl ordering. Their equivalence is shown by using a differentialequation satisfied by the normal ordered vacuum.